    "body": "@non-fungible-nelson, I started looking into this.\r\nFrom what I see writerWithDefaultPrettyPrinter is called from 2 different utility classes ([JsonUtil](https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/a46cf27ec5cfee049e627614ab345b0ed4f172c4/config/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/config/JsonUtil.java#L331C27-L331C27) and [JsonUtils](https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/a46cf27ec5cfee049e627614ab345b0ed4f172c4/ethereum/evmtool/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/evmtool/JsonUtils.java#L38)), however both are in different modules and have different command interfaces (BesuCommand and  EvmToolCommand). The second one it's easy to update with a command argument but for the first one the things are a lot complicated as I can't find any proper configuration class referred inside BesuCommand that could help.\r\nCould you share your thoughts about this? what might be a possible hint?",
